      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows its age in a few areas. The engine starts up and runs consistently, and the transmission is functional, though it lacks the crispness of a newer model. You will notice some cosmetic wear on the interior upholstery and a few minor scuffs and dings on the exterior. It is a solid, honest car for someone looking for affordable transportation, but please expect to perform some routine maintenance in the near future to keep it in good working order.",
