    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Hi there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my car, and it\u2019s been such a reliable companion! It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved over the years. You\u2019ll find it runs smoothly and still looks great pulling into the driveway. It\u2019s perfect for someone who wants a dependable ride that\u2019s ready to hit the road today. I\u2019d love for you to come by, take it for a test drive, and see how nicely it handles!",
      "price": 32500.0,
